  ./COVERAGE.md:205:| `com.google.inject.extensions:guice-servlet` | [3.0<br>- 4.2.3](metadata/com.google.inject.extensions/guice-servlet/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Guice Servlet extends Google Guice for Java servlet applications, adding request and session scopes plus servlet and filter binding support. It integrates Guice-managed dependency injection into servlet containers through APIs such as ServletModule, GuiceFilter, and GuiceServletContextListener.</details> | [100.0% (0/0 calls)](stats/com.google.inject.extensions/guice-servlet/) |
  ./COVERAGE.md:302:| `com.sun.jersey.contribs:jersey-guice` | [1.9<br>- 1.19.4](metadata/com.sun.jersey.contribs/jersey-guice/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Jersey Guice integrates Jersey 1.x with Google Guice, letting JAX-RS resources and providers be constructed and injected through a Guice Injector. It supplies a servlet container and component provider so Guice-managed services can be used in Jersey web applications.</details> | [100.0% (6/6 calls)](stats/com.sun.jersey.contribs/jersey-guice/) |
  ./COVERAGE.md:1054:| `org.eclipse.sisu:org.eclipse.sisu.inject` | [0.3.0.M1<br>- 0.3.5](metadata/org.eclipse.sisu/org.eclipse.sisu.inject/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Eclipse Sisu Inject is a JSR-330 dependency injection container built on Google Guice that supports classpath scanning, auto-binding, and dynamic auto-wiring. It lets applications discover named components and wire missing dependencies without requiring explicit Guice module bindings for every component.</details> | [99.6% (223/224 calls)](stats/org.eclipse.sisu/org.eclipse.sisu.inject/) |
  ./COVERAGE.md:1389:| `org.sonatype.sisu:sisu-guice` | [2.1.7<br>- 2.9.0](metadata/org.sonatype.sisu/sisu-guice/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Sisu Guice is Sonatype's patched build of Google Guice, a lightweight Java dependency injection framework. It provides the com.google.inject API and runtime for binding, scoping, provider lookup, and object graph creation in Sisu-based applications.</details> | [50.6% (43/85 calls)](stats/org.sonatype.sisu/sisu-guice/) |
  ./COVERAGE.md:1390:| `org.sonatype.sisu:sisu-inject-bean` | [1.4.2<br>- 2.4.1](metadata/org.sonatype.sisu/sisu-inject-bean/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Sisu Inject Bean is a legacy wrapper around Sonatype Sisu's JSR-330 bean support, packaging Guice-based bean discovery, binding, locating, conversion, and container integration classes for Java applications. It helps applications scan class spaces for annotated components and wire them into Guice injectors while exposing Sonatype-specific injection annotations and utilities.</details> | [100.0% (14/14 calls)](stats/org.sonatype.sisu/sisu-inject-bean/) |
